description: This story takes place in the early 1960s and pushes characters that forged France in the 60s, politicians and industry captains. Some used the Second World War to seat some sort of personal and historical legitimacy. But sooner or later, masks fall. With a crash and in blood…

deck: French comic.
description: After 400 000 years of reign, Man is now threatened by an animal revolution. Indeed, different species manifest aggressive behavior towards them. These attacks are said to be coordinated by an unknown signal coming from the bottom of the Pacific Ocean, in a location that has the reputation of being inaccessible, Horizon Deep. The company Innerspace, specialist of extreme conditions modern technology will have to act quickly because the signal is repeating itself at regular intervals. And it is getting stronger and stronger…
name: Deep

deck: French comic.
description: Following the increase in offences and crimes in the United States, the prisons are overcrowded. To cope with the problem, the American Government tests a new prison for the most dangerous criminals: the Deepwaterprison, a maritime abyss just off the Bermudas. Nine hundred metres higher, on the surface, an oil rig explodes and sinks, creating an unprecedented ecological catastrophe. A repair team is urgently sent into the deep waters. The only place to stay at this depth is the Deepwaterprison, where mutineers are planning their escape.
name: Deepwater Prison

deck: French comic.
description:
A little before the year 1000

Provence is prey to Sarasin pirates who spread fear on the southern French coast.

Hazar is a young pirate, brave and ambitious, with blonde hair and blue eyes. He accompanies his Muwallad brothers in their malfeasance on ground or at sea. During an attack, his adoptive father is savagely murder and he is accused of treachery. He will never be a “real” Mullawad ! Hazar will continuously claim his innocence, no matter the price !
name: Sarrasins !

deck: French comic.
description:
21 September, 2019 - 13h13m:

The Atlantis shuttle disappears mysteriously from the control screens.

22 September, 2019 -13h13m:

All the timepieces (watches, clocks…) on the planet suddenly stop.

And that’s just a beginning...As the threat of the Apocalypse hangs over the whole planet, it would seem that the future of Humanity has plunged into obscurity…presaging the worst for our civilisation.
name: Prométhée
